abstract: College Basketball Roundup; Clemson men's basketball team defeats Duke, 68-63; other men's and women's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The Tigers now have consecutive victories over ranked opponents for the first time since the 1989 season.

headline.main: Clemson, on a Roll, Edges Past No. 9 Duke
